### Citation Requirement

If you use this project, in whole or in part, in your academic work (e.g., publications, theses, presentations, or derivative educational materials), **you must cite the authors** appropriately. Please use the following citation:

> Keshani K, Castro Vargas P, Gustini B, MohammadNejad Aynede A, Dobrokhotov I, Otoijamun F. *DRD_2025_Project: Educational pipeline for DNA methylation analysis*. University of Bologna, 2025. GitHub: https://github.com/kianinsilico/DRD_2025_Project

If you are unsure how to cite this work, please contact the authors via GitHub Issues.

